  textData:
  - You can move your units by dragging them to the destination or by clicking on
    them first and then clicking on the destination tile.
  - By clicking on an enemy you can see his stats and inventory in the top info screen.
  - By dragging on an empty tile you can pan the camera.
  - When attacking an enemy head on, he will counterattack. By attacking from behind
    the enemy can't counter attack.
  - You can use an item by selecting a character and pressing on the item. If you
    instead drag the item you can use it on near allies as well.
  - Before equipping, watch the weapons weight. If its higher than the maxHP of your
    character he will get Stat penalties.
  - Each point of Attack will increase your characters damage by 1.
  - Each point of Defense will decrease incoming damage by 1.
  - Spd will increase your dodge chance by 2%.By having 50% more speed than the enemy
    you will get 1/2 bonus attacks.
  - Each point of Acc will increase your hit chance by 2%. It also increases the activation
    chance of a lot of skills
  - The MaxHP Value determines the characters constitution, which is needed to get
    less penalties for using stronger gear.
